{"tid":254870,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[墨香私服]重新回到端遊,召集巴打決戰潘朵拉墨香","createTime":"2017-05-23T13:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T16:26:01.000Z","uid":118529,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"846616840dce9ec4c98214b29916c762f9d75ae1","tid":254870,"uid":118529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"我都係一個墨香經典玩家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開始玩起,我仲記得果陣個個為咗技能點,仲要不斷去壓lv,升lv好快,但技能點同技能永遠追唔上,打怪一d都唔痛,後來放棄咗一段時間無玩,就出現咗墨香私服,果陣我都有投入私服度玩,好似寶寶墨香,大話墨香,YY墨香,風雲墨香等等,我都有玩過,果陣仲未有內掛添。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放棄咗墨香咁多年,突然心血來潮,想玩返墨香,網上搜尋又見到有個私服準備開,唔知有無香港人一齊玩呢?? <br />\n我將佢個介紹文複制過黎先....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/18518319_1470178466354318_2721942270595255986_o.jpg?oh=7a8d14ef16f34e54045577050d791a25&amp;oe=59B41EA7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F18518319_1470178466354318_2721942270595255986_o.jpg%3Foh%3D7a8d14ef16f34e54045577050d791a25%26oe%3D59B41EA7&h=7cfb18b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n潘朵拉墨香 全新界面 經典懷舊 6月2日 晚上7時 火爆公測 <br />\n內容： <br />\n以最人性化設置 最新界面 最新系統 逐一呈現，為廣大玩家打造經典原味仿官服墨香 <br />\n遊戲網站 : <a href=\"http://www.pandoramso.com/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pandoramso.com%2F%20&d=aWio27DJuOuyfsjc3mJj9wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f0c37275\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.pandoramso.com/ </a><br />\nFaceBook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pandoraMSO/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FpandoraMSO%2F&d=aWio27DJuOuyfsjc3mJj9wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5ade8b74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pandoraMSO/</a><br />\n《 經驗值50倍 技能點50倍 掉寶機率50倍 武功經驗值2000倍 等級上限99級》 <br />\n《1萬惡名以下(不論是否有榜)不爆裝備、不會被搶奪物品、不爆技能 》 <br />\n※最嚴格保證遊戲平衡，絕不售賣VIP系統及裝備，無須花錢亦可暢玩※ <br />\n※擁有全新徽章、角色羽翼、全新百寶武器，給你不一樣的視覺享受※ <br />\n※蘭州10分鐘12綁定元寶，每10分鐘自動派發，無須下線領取 ※ <br />\n※蚩牛、巨陵神BOSS寶箱直接開啟綁定元寶、高級裝備※ <br />\n※擁有最完美遊戲系統，安全鎖、內掛、錄影、斷線重連等等※ <br />\n※潘朵拉墨香嚴禁任何外掛等軟件，只要啟動外掛無法進入遊戲 ※ <br />\n※祝福及組合※ <br />\n※武器最高攻擊/一擊+9※防具最高數值+300血.護.內※首飾最高可跳9力.敏.體.心※ <br />\n※1-30武器防具100%+9※31-50武器防具 100%+7※ <br />\n※51-81武器防具 100%+5※82-99武器防具 100%+3※ <br />\n※心動不如行動，6月2日晚上7時趕快加入潘朵拉墨香盡情狂歡※ <br />\n遊戲網站 : <a href=\"http://www.pandoramso.com/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pandoramso.com%2F%20&d=aWio27DJuOuyfsjc3mJj9wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f0c37275\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.pandoramso.com/ </a><br />\nFaceBook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pandoraMSO/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FpandoraMSO%2F&d=aWio27DJuOuyfsjc3mJj9wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=5ade8b74\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pandoraMSO/</a><br />\n<br />\n《潘朵拉墨香5大承諾》<br />\n1)不售賣任何VIP會員或裝備及遊戲道具，贊助只可購買元寶。<br />\n2)不開放新技能，不開放武器成長系統，不開放裝備組合寶石。<br />\n3)所有道具綁定元寶亦可獲得，無須花錢亦可暢玩遊戲。<br />\n4)完美開放攻城戰.要塞戰.生還者激鬥.江湖爭霸戰。<br />\n5)公眾假期日子雙倍綁定元寶！"},{"pid":"34f349e37870bff8f13f63fb02c23697d5b68c1c","tid":254870,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"以前無祝武<br />\n正服渣把41+7武已經好威<br />\n當年祝福石未普及<br />\n一隻強50up既護手已經好值錢"},{"pid":"b3aeff9467b822ec4edb72aabf58b99a11f0d5a2","tid":254870,"uid":55382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T13:56:10.000Z","msg":"開到暑假完 呃晒班傻仔課金 收皮 換名再開 無限loop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.